Class MapData

  • java.lang.Object
    • MapData

  • public class MapData
extends java.lang.Object
    This MapData class is a remodification of project 2's MapData class but with different variable types. This class reads in a textfile and parses the Max,Min, and Average of the following data types: SRAD, TAIR, and TA9M. The class also displays their STID as well.
    Version:
    2018-10-29
    Author:
    Triston Luzanta
